Johannesburg- Twitter has handed flowers to radio personality and DJ, Dineo Ranaka for her magnificent job as the executive producer of one of the most talked-about television shows, Mzali wam. Mzali wam season 2 is a drama series that airs at 8pm every Monday on Mzansi Magic. Ranaka who recently graduated as sangoma, has produced shows like Dineo’s Diary, a reality television show about her life, and her family’s reality television show, The Ranakas.  “All credit goes to all actors and actresses, all of the production team, all crew and all at channel (our valued client) for trusting us with this entity. What a stellar team. I’m proud of the growth of my production house Brains At Work Media. Let’s do more! WAY more!” she wrote on her Instagram page.  Take a look at the praise that flowed in for Ranaka on social media below:        For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here. 